NOTE ON ADAPTED MATERIAL

This project's narrative structure is inspired by "The Contract: A One-Shot
Adventure in D&D 5th Edition" by Lucas Zellers (2020), Scintilla Studio
(https://scintilla.studio). The Contract PDF itself is (c) Lucas Zellers and
is not redistributed. This adaptation is a personal learning/teaching project
and reimplements the random-plot one-shot pattern in a novel voxel game form;
specific text, names, and stat blocks from the source are paraphrased or
replaced. For any commercial or public release, contact the original author
at lucas@scintilla.studio.

D&D, Dungeons & Dragons, and related trademarks are property of Wizards of
the Coast LLC. This is an unofficial fan project, not affiliated with WotC.
